methods.name: NextBool

parameters.name: invProbability
parameters.notes: The inverse probability of returning TRUE. The one in- chance.

methods.notes:
Returns random TRUE or FALSE, based on the inverse probability value supplied.

  Basically, returns TRUE if the next rand(invProbability) returns 0.
  eg.
   NextBool(10) has a one in 10 chance of returning TRUE.

Rand.PZSeedGenerator.notes:
Custom class to disable DevRandomSeedGenerator() on Linux since it can block forever, and disable
 RandomDotOrgSeedGenerator() since it connects to the internet.
